      public Event(String name, String date, String time, String location, String eventDetails, int maxParticipants, ArrayList<String> waitList, Boolean geolocation, String organizerID)
      Event class storing metadata about events that users want to enter or create
      Parameters:
      name - The name of the event
      date - The date that the event is going to occur
      time - The time for which the event will happen
      location - Where the event is taking place
      eventDetails - Any extra notes from the organizer
      maxParticipants - Optional capacity limit on number of people who can participate in the event
      waitList - A list of entrants who want to enter the event
      geolocation - Boolean to determine if the organizer would like to check entrant location for attending event

      qrCodeData - A string used to represent the qr code
      organizerID - A string used to hold the android ID of the organizer
